#: ../../../doc/en/reference/plugin_list.rst:7
msgid ""
"Below is an automated compilation of ``pytest``` plugins available on `PyPI "
"<https://pypi.org>`_. It includes PyPI projects whose names begin with "
"\"pytest-\" and a handful of manually selected projects. Packages classified "
"as inactive are excluded."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/reference/plugin_list.rst:11
msgid ""
"For detailed insights into how this list is generated, please refer to `the "
"update script <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/blob/main/scripts/update-"
"plugin-list.py>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/reference/plugin_list.rst:16
msgid ""
"Please be aware that this list is not a curated collection of projects and "
"does not undergo a systematic review process. It serves purely as an "
"informational resource to aid in the discovery of ``pytest`` plugins."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/reference/plugin_list.rst:20
msgid ""
"Do not presume any endorsement from the ``pytest`` project or its "
"developers, and always conduct your own quality assessment before "
"incorporating any of these plugins into your own projects."
msgstr ""

